-Complete stages and unlock incredible new golf challenges to conquer by winning real-time golf battles
-Master your golf swing with precision and creativity to watch your skills grow

-Multiplayer mode, mini golf mode and other challenges await for you to play every day
-Beautiful 3D golf courses of different themes and difficulties will always present a realistic golf challenge

-Win to unlock amazing rewards to take onto the course for your next round and enhance your golf bag
-With every exciting real-time golf clash, you’ll gain important skills and tricks to hit extreme golf shots!

INFINITE GOLF FUN
-Every Golf Rival season is fun and fresh, with new courses, balls and rewards appearing all the time!
-Golf ball games and skill games like Kingdom, Ace Open, Brink Game and more provide you with many fun spins on classic golf.

Collect powerful golf clubs and balls and tee off across over 300+ courses in more than 20+ themes! Satisfy your golf dreams of hitting incredible shots, climbing the leaderboards and proving you’re a golf game master. Let’s go for a perfect swing and hit that hole-in-one, golfers!

From 1v1 PvP golf, to Tournament mode where it’s you against the community of golfers around the world, to playing golf with friends - in Golf Rival, scoring a birdie is only the start of the competitive fun! Use powerful balls and clubs to outwit your opponent, as no two fun multiplayer golf battles are the same.

Grab your golf clubs, because Golf Rival has it all, whether you’re a golfing games newbie or an ultimate sports game expert!

PLAY EXCITING GOLF GAMES
-Complete stages and unlock incredible new golf challenges to conquer by winning real-time golf battles
-Master your golf swing with precision and creativity to watch your skills grow
-Compete in both 9-hole and 18-hole Tournaments in every exciting season
-Multiplayer mode and other challenges await for you to play every day
-Beautiful 3D golf courses of different themes and difficulties will always present an ultimate golf challenge

-Win to unlock amazing rewards to take onto the course for your next round and enhance your golf bag
-With every exciting real-time golf clash, you’ll gain important skills and tricks to hit extreme golf shots!

INFINITE GOLF FUN
-Every Golf Rival season is fun and fresh, with new courses, balls and rewards appearing all the time!
-Golf ball games and skill games like Kingdom, Ace Open, Brink Game and more provide you with many fun spins on classic golf.
-Add your friends and see who has the swag golf skills needed to become the #1 golfer!

Join golf fans around the world and download Golf Rival to get started on your way to becoming an ultimate golf game champion!
